Params: {1: '1', 3: 'You see supplementary data blocks here and there in this area. After walking for some time, you see another data blockade standing in your way.'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: '...So this space was intentionally separated as a storage space for all the supplementary data blocks?', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Well... I guess we'll just have to do the same thing again.", 4: '22'}
{3: 'The space behind the blockade becomes accessible again when the blockade is deactivated.'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: '"Bianca" is most likely... just right up ahead.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Let's go. Brace yourself. I've got a feeling that it's not going to be the smoothest ride.", 4: '3'}
